{
  "stem": "14552.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in-- those little huts were assigned to people, where on the way to-- to the brick factory, the Germans were with their whips, were very cruel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were hitting people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were-- they were just as-- like animals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were the animals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I carried so much stuff that I felt my arches were like breaking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said-- I still say it-- could be wrong, but my-- my feet got injured from carrying all that weight on-- on my-- I was very thin.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never eat much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't have a big appetite as a child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Oh, I-- I got an appetite when it was-- there was nothing to eat anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I thought I could eat by then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I was very skinny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- I have a feeling that my arches have-- have been injured by carrying all that stuff.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now we get to the-- through all that unbelievable attrition, we got to the brick factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there they start to punish us again with taking people out and beating them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And girls were raped there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother hid me in the-- my sister and I-- she hid us in the-- in the little hut.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she gave me a scarf.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She put a scarf on me and wrapped up my head so that my face would hardly show.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she stuck me in there, and don't you dare leave, because they were-- they did their-- their punitive, their attrition, their--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their brutality that they were given reign and freedom and encouragement, which they needed very little of.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then after a few days, we were herded into coal and cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germans.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germans with the Hungarians together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans were-- they had now the orders to-- to ship these people to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
